channel.title: Ebay recognized me ^^
channel.description:
Lol, just felt like posting this, see if it was really me or not, got this message today, http://mixscape.info/Gallery/main.php?g2_view=core.DownloadItem&g2_itemId=442&g2_GALLERYSID=04dfcae41722eb8ae529d1df4cd3703e and when i saw the sellers buzz near the bottom right, i just busted out laughing, because recently me and a friend sold a completely broken ipod, said it was broken and all, as is, and it sold, http://mixscape.info/Gallery/main.php?g2_view=core.DownloadItem&g2_itemId=444&g2_serialNumber=1
any one seen any others go for 65$, i just wanna see if it was really mine they where talking about.
